<section xmlns:codified="https://code.dccouncil.us/schemas/codified" xmlns:codify="https://code.dccouncil.us/schemas/codify" xmlns:xi="http://www.w3.org/2001/XInclude" containing-doc="D.C. Code">
  <num>2-102</num>
  <heading>“Person” defined.</heading>
  <text>Wherever the word “person” is used in this subchapter it shall include individuals, firms, partnerships, associations, and corporations.</text>
